{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775882968595,"sessionID":"ses_285208642ffeRWhsZ7Dp5Y3CSj","part":{"id":"prt_d7adf9df3001N9Y2LoZ6Zqxn1T","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d7adf8993001gD1so5LHDuEfIj","sessionID":"ses_285208642ffeRWhsZ7Dp5Y3CSj","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":21871,"input":6640,"output":192,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":15039}},"cost":0}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775882973996,"sessionID":"ses_285208642ffeRWhsZ7Dp5Y3CSj","part":{"id":"prt_d7adfb32b001T3FnyeQMeUzz1G","messageID":"msg_d7adf9e2b001h4Wq7DiJA69QDv","sessionID":"ses_285208642ffeRWhsZ7Dp5Y3CSj","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882975732,"sessionID":"ses_285208642ffeRWhsZ7Dp5Y3CSj","part":{"id":"prt_d7adfb75c001F55pBRBTw5Hu83","messageID":"msg_d7adf9e2b001h4Wq7DiJA69QDv","sessionID":"ses_285208642ffeRWhsZ7Dp5Y3CSj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-b30872b5d65e40a2bb61e4c97d959bc5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-030/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-030/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: Helm Chart for AgentCube platform provides a standardized, configurable, and reusable Kubernetes deployment solution. The chart encapsulates all necessary Kubernetes resources (CRDs, Deployments, Services, ConfigMaps, RBAC) and enables flexible configuration through Values files, simplifying deployment across multiple environments.\n6: \n7: **Module:** `manifests`  \n8: **Language:** YAML + Go Templates  \n9: **Source Root:** `manifests/charts/agentcube/`  \n10: **Size:** L\n11: \n12: ## Architecture\n13: \n14: ### Chart Structure\n15: \n16: ```\n17: agentcube/\n18: ├── Chart.yaml                          # Chart metadata\n19: ├── values.yaml                         # Default configuration\n20: ├── values-dev.yaml                     # Development environment overrides\n21: ├── values-prod.yaml                    # Production environment overrides\n22: ├── values-test.yaml                    # Test environment overrides\n23: ├── templates/\n24: │   ├── crds/\n25: │   │   ├── agentruntime.yaml           # AgentRuntime CRD\n26: │   │   └── codeinterpreter.yaml        # CodeInterpreter CRD\n27: │   ├── controller-manager/\n28: │   │   ├── deployment.yaml             # Controller Manager deployment\n29: │   │   ├── service.yaml                # Controller Manager service\n30: │   │   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # Controller Manager service account\n31: │   │   └── rbac.yaml                   # Controller Manager RBAC rules\n32: │   ├── workload-manager/\n33: │   │   ├── deployment.yaml             # Workload Manager deployment\n34: │   │   ├── service.yaml                # Workload Manager service\n35: │   │   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # Workload Manager service account\n36: │   │   └── rbac.yaml                   # Workload Manager RBAC rules\n37: │   ├── router/\n38: │   │   ├── deployment.yaml             # Router deployment\n39: │   │   ├── service.yaml                # Router service\n40: │   │   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # Router service account\n41: │   │   └── rbac.yaml                   # Router RBAC rules\n42: │   ├── rbac/\n43: │   │   ├── clusterrole.yaml            # Cluster-wide role\n44: │   │   └── clusterrolebinding.yaml     # Cluster-wide role binding\n45: │   ├── monitoring/\n46: │   │   └── servicemonitor.yaml         # Prometheus ServiceMonitor\n47: │   ├── configmaps/\n48: │   │   └── config.yaml                 # Application configuration\n49: │   ├── secrets/\n50: │   │   └── secret.yaml                 # Sensitive configuration\n51: │   ├── networkpolicies/\n52: │   │   └── networkpolicy.yaml          # Network access control\n53: │   ├── poddisruptionbudgets/\n54: │   │   ├── controller-manager.yaml\n55: │   │   ├── workload-manager.yaml\n56: │   │   └── router.yaml\n57: │   ├── NOTES.txt                       # Installation notes\n58: │   ├── _helpers.tpl                    # Template helpers\n59: │   └── ingress.yaml                    # Ingress configuration\n60: ├── tests/\n61: │   ├── controller-manager_test.yaml\n62: │   ├── workload-manager_test.yaml\n63: │   └── router_test.yaml\n64: └── README.md                           # Chart documentation\n65: ```\n66: \n67: ### Component Interactions\n68: \n69: ```\n70: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n71: │                      Helm Chart                             │\n72: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐     │\n73: │  │   CRDs       │  │  Controller  │  │   Workload   │     │\n74: │  │              │  │   Manager    │  │   Manager    │     │\n75: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘     │\n76: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐     │\n77: │  │    Router    │  │    RBAC      │  │  Monitoring  │     │\n78: │  │              │  │              │  │              │     │\n79: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘     │\n80: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n81:                               │\n82:                               │ helm install/upgrade\n83:                               ▼\n84: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n85: │                   Kubernetes Cluster                        │\n86: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n87: │  │              API Server + etcd                       │  │\n88: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n89: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐     │\n90: │  │  Controller  │  │   Workload   │  │    Router    │     │\n91: │  │   Manager    │  │   Manager    │  │              │     │\n92: │  │   (Pods)     │  │   (Pods)     │  │   (Pods)     │     │\n93: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘     │\n94: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐     │\n95: │  │   Services   │  │     CRDs     │  │   Secrets/   │     │\n96: │  │              │  │              │  │  ConfigMaps  │     │\n97: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘     │\n98: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n99: ```\n100: \n101: ## Data Structures\n102: \n103: ### Chart.yaml\n104: \n105: ```yaml\n106: apiVersion: v2\n107: name: agentcube\n108: description: Helm chart for AgentCube platform - Kubernetes-native AI agent runtime and code interpreter\n109: type: application\n110: version: 1.0.0\n111: appVersion: \"1.0.0\"\n112: keywords:\n113:   - agentcube\n114:   - ai\n115:   - code-interpreter\n116:   - agent-runtime\n117:   - kubernetes\n118: maintainers:\n119:   - name: AgentCube Team\n120:     email: team@agentcube.io\n121: home: https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n122: sources:\n123:   - https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n124: icon: https://agentcube.io/logo.svg\n125: annotations:\n126:   artifacthub.io/category: ai-machine-learning\n127:   artifacthub.io/license: Apache-2.0\n128:   artifacthub.io/operator: \"false\"\n129: ```\n130: \n131: ### Values.yaml Hierarchy\n132: \n133: ```yaml\n134: # Global configuration applied to all components\n135: global:\n136:   imageRegistry: docker.io\n137:   imagePullSecrets: []\n138:   namespaceOverride: agentcube\n139:   labels: {}\n140:   annotations: {}\n141: \n142: # Image pull policy for all components\n143: imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n144: \n145: # Controller Manager configuration\n146: controllerManager:\n147:   enabled: true\n148:   replicaCount: 2\n149:   image:\n150:     repository: agentcube/controller-manager\n151:     tag: v1.0.0\n152:     pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n153:   service:\n154:     type: ClusterIP\n155:     port: 8080\n156:     targetPort: 8080\n157:     annotations: {}\n158:   resources:\n159:     requests:\n160:       cpu: 100m\n161:       memory: 128Mi\n162:     limits:\n163:       cpu: 500m\n164:       memory: 512Mi\n165:   nodeSelector: {}\n166:   tolerations: []\n167:   affinity: {}\n168:   podAnnotations: {}\n169:   podLabels: {}\n170:   securityContext:\n171:     runAsNonRoot: true\n172:     runAsUser: 1000\n173:     fsGroup: 1000\n174:   containerSecurityContext:\n175:     allowPrivilegeEscalation: false\n176:     capabilities:\n177:       drop:\n178:         - ALL\n179:     readOnlyRootFilesystem: true\n180:   livenessProbe:\n181:     httpGet:\n182:      